devdoc.author: Suresh Konakanchi
devdoc.details: Library for managing all customers, who are involved in the KYC process

returns.exists_: boolean value to say if customer exists or not

getcustomerdetails(address).details: To get details of the customer

returns._0: Customer object which will have complete details of the customer

searchcustomers(address,address[]).details: Search for customer details in the list that the bank is directly linked to

returns._0: boolean to say if customer exists or not
returns._1: Customer object to get the complete details of the customer Costly operation if we had more customers linked to this single bank

updatedatahash(string,uint256).details: Updates the Datahash of the documents

params.currentTime_: Current Date Time in unix epoch timestamp
params.hash_: Data hash value that need to be updated

params.email_: Email that need to be updated
params.mobile_: Mobile number that need to be updated
